{
  "stem": "3097.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Whatever happened to this, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I had two guns-- actually, two guns.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One had seven bullets, and the other one had three bullets, the-- what I found in the-- in the coal.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I decided to escape.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I selected a day, a lucky day-- the 12th of May-- because I finished school at that time.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "People watched me like a hawk-- the mafia, even the fellow who is alive, my friend, who brought me the documents to-- to my city to escape, he belonged also to the mafia there, you know?",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE], you know?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He lives in Canada now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They watched, because they knew that I had family outside, that I'm trying to escape.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But they were afraid to do anything, you see?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was like-- like United States with Russia, with it's-- with the nuclear bombs, you see?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So they watched me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it so happened that I developed an abscess on my knuckle here.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I was limping a little bit, and I started to exaggerate.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I made the date the 12th of May.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the 12th of May, we decided to escape.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The nurse, not [INAUDIBLE], was not anymore a-- a nurse.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Her girlfriend, [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Renya ?] Kenisberg who lives now in-- in Sweden, was the nurse.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because the chief of the plant decided we don't need two nurses.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when I was transferred, I was working on the night shift, and Wasser also on the night shift.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was supposed to go out from the barracks and meet us by the latrine, because the wires of the latrine-- you see, the latrines, they jut out a little from the wires.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because the Poles used to come, then empty outside the-- you know, the residual stays, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
